item.description: const main = async () = { const res = await fetch("https://weather-adlpwp4faq-du.a.run.app/"); const data = await res.json(); const spec = { "config": {"view": {"continuousWidth": 500, "continuousHeight": 300}}, "data": {"name": "data"}, "mark": "line", "encoding": { "x": { "type": "temporal", "field": "dt", }, "y": {"type": "quantitative", "field": "aqi"}, }, "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v4.8.1.json", "datasets": { "data": data, }, }; vegaEmbed("#vega-view", spec); }; main();
